@tacigar @adriancole I was playing around today and found a solution that fixes the above mentioned bug. If we completely un-mount and re-mount VizceralExt, it re-renders with the correct layout -> 
![zipkin-vizceral-2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20159504/67332558-0d9abe80-f4d4-11e9-9c92-5ad42b8106c9.gif) 

It's not the most elegant solution, as it hacks thorough some of the react re-rendering magic, but fixes the "stacking" issue. Let me know what you think
